{10000}{}{We've all been boxed up into these flying thingies and delivered to their base in the middle of the ocean. "Enclave", that's how they named selves. We were kept inside force fields and couldn't do anything. Well no one really wanted to. [Bob spits on the floor scornfully] Cowards. But I'm not like that, @sex@|dude||babe|.}
