{11000}{}{I came up with the plan! A pefect one! It was simple and genial... But I didn't get a chance to materialize it 'cause that Chose One showed up. [Bob bevels like he just swallowed 10 lemons at once] Can you imagine what he's done? That butch kicked them "steel guys" asses and freed us! It's like, my plan was just rolled up and stuck into a gecko's arse.}
